<h2>7. Grammarly — Best AI Tool for Writing Quality</h2>
<p>Grammarly has evolved far beyond spell-checking. The 2026 version includes AI writing assistance, tone adjustment, plagiarism detection, and brand voice consistency. For small businesses where written communication matters — which is all of them — Grammarly is essential.</p>
